data.description: "Luxuriate" is the operative word for 2661 Annapolis Circle. From the expansive nearly-new $30k paver patio out back to the open-plan kitchen with quartz countertops, gas range, and soft-close cabinets. From newer hand-scraped wood flooring and neutral tone paint; from soft light filtering through plantation shutters to coffered ceilings in the family room. The primary suite features bonus sitting room, tray ceiling, and oversized bathroom. All that, plus generous bedrooms, walking-distance to Kellam High School, and just minutes to the Municipal Complex, golf, and less than 10 miles to Sandbridge Beach.
